entry.title: WHITE SMOOCH BAND
entry.summary:
Vendor: SuzieB Fitness
Type: Glute Band
Price: 20.00

MEDIUM/HEAVY - STRONGEST RESISTANCE BAND 

Time to work on that peach! Shown are woven loop "Glute" bands featuring grips on the interior side of the band to prevent rolling up. Perfect for travel, and any kind of gym workout! Check Instagram for Suzie's band videos to see how it is used.

The Suzieb Glute Band is made with woven material, smooch print, and a rubber label featured on the seam. It comes in a printed poly bag.  

Both smooch bands are limited edition! Once they are sold out, they will be gone!

ALL SALES FINAL
